item.title: I need help with turning server on
item.dc:creator: @the1337legend the1337legend
item.description:
@the1337legend wrote:

mmmm if u be most descriptive i could help:
CHECK THAT U DID THIS:

  • Download JDK6 Update 12
  • Make A No-Ip
  • Download No-Ip DUC
  • Check To See What Ip Duc Is Using, And Compare To The Ip On Your Router Page
  • Compiled Your Server (EVERYTHING MUST BE CLOSED FIRST)
  • Does It Say “(server name here) IS RUNNING”?
  • On Your Client Are You Using YOUR SERVER IP?
  • On Your Client Try Using 127.0.1.1 as the server ip, if you can connect, that means u didnt portforward correctly.

tell meh if u neeedz anything (.)_(.)
